---
import InfoLayout from '../layouts/InfoLayout.astro';
---

<InfoLayout
  title="Privacy Policy · StudentLancers"
  description="How StudentLancers collects, uses, and protects your data."
  eyebrow="Legal"
  heading="Privacy Policy"
  lead="Last updated: June 5, 2026. We collect the minimum data needed to make the marketplace work, and we never sell it."
>
  <h2>What we collect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Account data:</strong> name, email, role (student or company), password (hashed).</li>
    <li><strong>Verification data:</strong> your .edu or work email confirmation, plus optional portfolio links.</li>
    <li><strong>Engagement data:</strong> briefs you post, applications you submit, messages, and files shared in the workspace.</li>
    <li><strong>Payment data:</strong> handled by Stripe. We never see your card number.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>How we use it</h2>
  <p>
    To match students with briefs, run escrow, and contact you about your
    account. We do not sell your data, and we do not share it with
    third-party advertisers.
  </p>

  <h2>Cookies</h2>
  <p>
    We use one functional cookie to keep you signed in. We use a small
    set of analytics cookies to understand which pages need work. See our
    <a href="/cookies">Cookies page</a> for the full list.
  </p>

  <h2>Your rights</h2>
  <p>
    You can export, correct, or delete your data at any time from account
    settings. Email <a href="mailto:privacy@studentlancers.com">privacy@studentlancers.com</a>
    and we will respond within five business days.
  </p>

  <h2>Security</h2>
  <p>
    We encrypt data in transit and at rest, hash passwords, and run annual
    third-party security reviews. See our <a href="/security">Security page</a>
    for the full report.
  </p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>
    Questions? <a href="/contact">Get in touch</a> or email
    <a href="mailto:privacy@studentlancers.com">privacy@studentlancers.com</a>.
  </p>
</InfoLayout>
